listitem.para:
This option will add custom options to the main menu. It is an array of arrays listing the caption, access level required, and the link to be executed. For example:
$g_main_menu_custom_options = array( array( 'title' => 'My Link', 'access_level' => MANAGER, 'url' => 'my_link.php', 'icon' => 'fa-plug' ), array( 'title' => 'My Link2', 'access_level' => ADMINISTRATOR, 'url' => 'my_link2.php', 'icon' => 'fa-plug' ) );
Note that if the caption is found in custom_strings_inc.php (see ), it will be replaced by the corresponding translated string. Options will only be added to the menu if the current logged in user has the appropriate access level.
